<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Coach Hill</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A tranquil neighborhood in the South-West Calgary originally built in the 1970s Coach Hill homes have undergone a series of transformations to evolve into a well developed urban community with an eclectic mix of housing styles.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Spread across an area of 1.1 square kilometer, the community in Coach Hill boasts of luscious green parks and gardens that render it one of the most breathtaking housing locations in the whole of Calgary.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">A large community center located nearby offers countless entertainment and recreational facilities such as playgrounds and baseball diamonds.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Given its convenient location and comfortable access to the Downtown, boutique stores and a host of recreational facilities, the Coach Hill real estate is fast becoming a hot favorite among modern home buyers.</p>
        </div>
